Comment: The glyph data itself is public domain: the classic
 IBM-PC-style 8x8 set from Marcel Sondaar's public-domain font8_8.asm
 (VGA fonts credited to Sondaar and IBM), packaged as font8x8_basic by
 Daniel Hepper's font8x8 project <https://github.com/dhepper/font8x8>.
 The GPL-3+ claim covers the file as shipped in vp; the underlying font
 data remains public domain.

